— MARLOWE VANCE, EDITOR & ONLY EAR</p>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"196\">\n        <div data-kid=\"197\">\n          <div class=\"lime border-b border-[#C6FF00] pb-2 mb-3\" data-kid=\"198\">SECTIONS</div>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-2 bone/70\" data-kid=\"199\">\n            <li data-kid=\"200\"><a href=\"#crate\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"201\">Reviews</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"202\"><a href=\"#rail\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"203\">Scenes</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"204\"><a href=\"#featured\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"205\">Features</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"206\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"207\">Archive</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"208\">\n          <div class=\"lime border-b border-[#C6FF00] pb-2 mb-3\" data-kid=\"209\">RATINGS</div>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-2 bone/70\" data-kid=\"210\">\n            <li data-kid=\"211\">9.0+ Essential</li>\n            <li data-kid=\"212\">7.0–8.9 Strong</li>\n            <li data-kid=\"213\">5.0–6.9 Flawed</li>\n            <li data-kid=\"214\">&lt;5.0 Skip It</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"215\">\n          <div class=\"lime border-b border-[#C6FF00] pb-2 mb-3\" data-kid=\"216\">SIGNAL</div>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-2 bone/70\" data-kid=\"217\">\n            <li data-kid=\"218\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"219\">Newsletter</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"220\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"221\">RSS</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"222\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"223\">Bandcamp</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"224\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#C6FF00]\" data-kid=\"225\">Submit Promo</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"border-t-2 border-[#F5F3EE] mt-16 pt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-4 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest bone/50\" data-kid=\"226\">\n      <span data-kid=\"227\">© 2026 THE PLATTER — NO STREAMING, NO MERCY</span>\n      <span data-kid=\"228\">MASTERED AT 33⅓ RPM</span>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n\n</div>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"229\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"230\"></script>\n<script data-kid=\"231\">\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n  // hero headline stagger\n  gsap.from(\".hl\", { y: 120, opacity: 0, duration: 0.9, ease: \"power4.out\", stagger: 0.12, delay: 0.2 });\n\n  // vinyl always spins slowly (no hover speed-up)\n\n  // section titles slide in with kinetic offset\n  gsap.utils.toArray(\".reveal-title\").forEach((el) => {\n    gsap.from(el, {\n      x: -80, opacity: 0, duration: 0.8, ease: \"power3.out\",\n      scrollTrigger: { trigger: el, start: \"top 85%\" }\n    });\n  });\n\n  // crate cards rise\n  gsap.utils.toArray(\".crate-card\").forEach((el, i) => {\n    gsap.from(el, {\n      y: 90, opacity: 0, duration: 0.7, ease: \"power3.out\",\n      scrollTrigger: { trigger: el, start: \"top 90%\" }\n    });\n  });\n</script></div>\n  \n  \n",
